    },
    {
      "point": "Absence of hyperparameter sensitivity analysis for CCL's weighting term (λ)",
      "evidence": "The paper provides no sensitivity analysis or clear justification for the chosen value of λ=1.0... presents no ablation studies varying λ nor any discussion regarding its impact on performance."
    },
    {
      "point": "Narrow scope of OOD evaluation and unaddressed generalizability gap",
      "evidence": "The evaluation primarily focuses on an OOD definition limited to 'novel classes' drawn from the same general domain... lacks any evaluation against truly out-of-domain datasets. The paper does not offer theoretical or empirical insights into how NP+CCL specifically addresses or mitigates the gap between synthetic and real-world OOD."
    },
    {
      "point": "Unquantified computational and financial costs of Novelty Prompting",
